	Local n.NPCs, n2.NPCs, d.Doors, de.Decals, r.Rooms, e.Events, w.WayPoints, p.Particles, wp.WayPoints, wayPointCloseToPlayer.WayPoints
	Local i%, j%, Dist#, Dist2#, Angle#, x#, x2#, y#, z#, z2#, PrevFrame#, PlayerSeeAble%, RN$
